{"tid":295331,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有九月去法國exchange的面孔","createTime":"2017-06-23T16:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T13:06:23.000Z","uid":460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"981ed975ad1e9ae309d54def7916d1dc94a0ce18","tid":295331,"uid":460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"仲有幾個月就要出發喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一個陌生地方生存幾個月 都希望有人係個邊互相照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚去用campus france既pre departure meeting 都見到有唔少人黎緊會去法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地開左個telegram group 大家可以入黎搵旅伴 搵flatmate 咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEHdRYqoEhw_yvwrQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEHdRYqoEhw_yvwrQA&d=133p1LRAIpg7kyuPimlQsi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d93fcee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEHdRYqoEhw_yvwrQA</a><br />\n<br />\n去之前記住要快d去申請visa<br />\n<br />\nLong stay visa申請流程<br />\n1. Send email去campus france 約academic interview<br />\n佢問既野其實好簡單 叫你簡單介紹自己 問你識唔識法文 點解會想去法國 去法國有d咩expectation等等<br />\n記住快d send email約interview 已經排期排到去7月尾<br />\n2. 上法國領事館網頁約整visa<br />\n記住帶齊所有document上去 帶多好過帶少 bank statement要夠錢 minimum每個月要有六百幾euro生活費 要買左保險，機票同埋有住址證明<br />\n3. 交齊所有資料等大約兩星期就可以拎visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492e70c6772ced3fd85e11a3a050c0c45c3a85fb","tid":295331,"uid":103442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺法國exchange返嚟，有咩想知可以問下我"},{"pid":"dade7f2c64d8aac295fc609d90eee096dda5c5db","tid":295331,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"be8cac7f79178851001852b969b7f772161c1c0c","tid":295331,"uid":460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"